Class Blade

java.lang.Object
Blade
public class Blade extends Object
This is a Blade component class for Bladed Weapon. This class serves as a class that represents all blades.

    • Blade

      public Blade(String name, Material mat, double length, double sharpness)
      Constructor for Blade class
      Parameters:
      name - The name for the blade template
      mat - The Material Object that represents the material for the blade
      length - The length of the blade in metres
      sharpness - The sharpness rating for the blade. Entire range of int is accepted but positive numbers preferred.

    • Blade

      public Blade(String name, String material, double length, double sharpness, double density)
      Constructor for Blade Class (verbose)
      Parameters:
      name - String name for the Blade template. The String will be trimmed before saving.
      material - String name for the material for the blade. Material naming rules observed.
      length - double length of the blade in metres. (Min 0.1) Negative numbers will be taken as positive.
      sharpness - The sharpness rating for the blade. (Min 1.0)
      density - The density of the material used for the blade. Material density rules observed.
      See Also:
      • Material
